  2. This privacy policy applies only to the actions of PayViaMe and Users with respect to the application and website. It does not extend to any other applications or websites that can be accessed from this PayViaMe including, but not limited to, any links we may provide to social media websites or externally-facing URLs provided throughout throughout the course of using PayViaMe . <br>
</p>
